    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Access </strong>Gem pony</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Trigger</strong> You use Quick Alchemy to craft an alchemical bomb with a level at least 1 lower than your advanced alchemy level.</p>\n<hr />\n<p dir=\"ltr\">You create a bomb that explodes into sharp shards of gems in addition to its usual effects. The direct target of the bomb gains 1d4 persistent piercing damage per die of damage of the bomb. Those caught in the splash gain 1 persistent piercing damage per die of the damage of the bomb. If the bomb already deals persistent damage, they are both applied.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"> </p>"
